==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Three
<hw>Three</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The number greater by a
unit than two; three units or objects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A symbol representing three units, as 3 or
iii.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Rule of three</b></col>. <fld>(Arith.)</fld> <cd>See
under <er>Rule</er>, <pos>n.</pos></cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

